transform_def.name: designed26
transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) s = sin(length(p_in) + sin(abs(p_in.x))) t = sin(length(p_in) + sin(abs(p_in.y))) u = lerp(s, t, 0.5) v = fmod(s / t * r / u, length(p_in) * cos(u)) z = u * v con1 = abs(z) < r con2 = abs(z) > r in (if if fill > 0.0 then con1 else con2 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
